                                                Bergherrn</rs>, 3. <rs type="person" ref="#pe__leopold_poltz_QGW_II_I_776">des <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__heinrich_von_der_neisse_QGW_II_I_459">Schwagers</roleName> des Ausstellers <roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Leupolts des Polczs,
                                                  <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien">statrichter</roleName> ze Wienn</rs>, 4. <rs type="person" ref="#pe__hartmann_metsakch_QGW_II_I_641"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Hartmans des
